Description: Implements Bayesian quantile regression approaches using the EM algorithm 
    and several MCMC methods with observation weights for complex survey designs. The package 
    provides two main functions: 'bqr.svy()' and 'mo.bqr.svy()'. Includes fast C++ implementations 
    using 'Rcpp', 'RcppArmadillo', and 'RcppEigen'.
